quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  26,137,"Pellet, …óum wonaali si wanaa jikku adinoo…ďe …ďen"
  26,138,Menen men wonaali leptoytee…ďe
  26,139,"∆Āe fenni mo, Men halki …ďe. Pellet, wonii e …óum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo] Aaya, …ďur…ďe heewude e ma…ď…ďe laataaki gom…óin…ďe"
  26,140,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa, ko Kanko woni Teddu…óo Yurmetee…óo"
  26,141,Samuudinkoo…ďe …ďen fenniino Nulaa…ďe …ďen
  26,142,"Tuma nde Saalihu musi…ó…óo ma…ď…ďe on wi'annoo …ďe: \"Enee, on hulataa [Alla]"
  26,143,"Min dey, ko mi Nulaa…óo e moo…óon hoolaa…óo"
  26,144,Hulee Alla …óofto…óon mi
  26,145,"Mi toraaki on e dow …óum njo…ďdi, njo…ďdi am ndin fawaaki si wanaa Jooma winndere nden"
  26,146,"Enee, hara on accete e koo ko woni …óoo ko on hoolii…ďe"
  26,147,E nder gese e can…ói
  26,148,E remuruuji e tamarooje hara dukke majje ko …ďenndu…óum
  26,149,"Hi…óon lesa pelle …óen [wa…óon] cuu…ói ko on haawitii…ďe"
  26,150,Hulee Alla …óofto…óon mi
  26,151,Wata on …óofto yamaruyee fantinoo…ďe …ďen
  26,152,∆Āen bonnoo…ďe ka leydi hara …ďe mo∆ī∆īintaa
  26,153,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Pellet, an ko a jeyaa…óo mbilaa…ďe …ďen"
  26,154,"An a wonaali si wanaa …ďanndunke yeru amen, awa addu Aaya, si tawii a laatike jeyaa…óo e goongu…ďe …ďen"
  26,155,"O maaki: \"Mbaa…óoo ko naaqawa, no woodani mba yaramnde, no woodani on onon kadi yaramnde √Īalaande anndaande"
  26,156,"Wata on memir mba ko boni, sakko nannga on Lepte √Ďalnde Mawnde"
  26,157,"∆Āe mborii mba, …ďe wonti nimsu…ďe"
  26,158,"Lepte …óen nanngi …ďe. Pellet, wonii e …óum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo] Aaya, …ďur…ďe heewude e ma…ď…ďe laataaki gom…óin…ďe"
  26,159,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa, ko Kanko woni Teddu…óo Yurmetee…óo"
